texts.text: >Someone's shouting in the park late at night...
Fuck the company and fuck management!
"With your talent and ability you should be able to find new employment in no time."
What a buncha bull!
OMG, is that guy drunk?
Whoa... He's shouting like a madman...
...What're you looking at?!

!!
C-C'mon, we're going to miss the last train home!
*Sigh*
WTF man... I busted my ass for that company...
They say that God only gives men trials that they can overcome...
But what have I done to deserve this?!
Why am I always the one to get the short end of the stick?!
What am I going to do now...? How am I supposed to break this to my family...
...Poor soul.
Huh?
>A voice can be heard coming from the darkness...
...I must be imagining things. Maybe I had a bit too much to drink...
That is not so. I exist, and I am here,
Huh...? E-Eek! W-What are you?!
>Looking closely into the darkness, the presence of the speaker can be felt...
You have nothing to fear from me, for I also am someone who has had enough of God's tyranny.
...So unreasonable bad things happened to you too?
Yes, that is true.
God, in His arrogance, think we are all but slaves to His whims.
He will not endow men with the means to struggle against their fortune.
And when things go wrong, He just washes everything away with a flood and act like nothing ever happened.
Oh... Isn't that from the Bible or something?
Sorry, I'm not really familiar with that kind of stuff.
It does not matter, for you are worthy.
Therefor, I will bestow upon you some knowledge.
K-Knowledge...?
>A hand emerges from the darkness and hands the man something...
A chain...?

!!
What is this? Oh...
This power...
Yes. This is the forbidden knowledge that God has been keeping from you humans...
With this power, you can mold your life to your own liking.
You can even overcome God and His minions if they try to interfere.
Not even He can hold you down now.
...Yes, with this power I can make the company and the executives take me back...
No, forget about working for some stupid company. I can be free...
Yes, you are free to use this power as you see fit.
But remember never to summon something beyond your ability to control.
Always be mindful of your own limits when using this knowledge, do you understand?
Hehehehe...
What? You really sure that that's what happened?
I saw it with my own eyes!
Yeah... But still... It's kinda hard to believe...
What's going on?
Is something wrong?
All hell's broken loose, that's what's going on!
EVERYTHING is wrong!
I just saw someone summon demons without using a smartphone!
Really? Are you sure that's what you saw?
Why won't anybody believe me?! You guys are driving me crazy!!
You sound pretty crazy already...
Aight! Aight!
I promise we'll take you seriously so tell us everything that you saw.
Okay, umm...
So I was on my way here after finishing my shift at the cafe,
and I saw some guy fighting demons.
I've never seen him before, but I figured he's a Dx2 right?
He was kinda on the losing end, so I jumped in to help him.
We were able to take down the demon, but...
The guy didn't know anything about either the Liberators or the Acolytes.
He's never even heard of the demon summoning app.
That's... pretty suspicious.
Yeah, that's why I wanted to stop and question him,
but he said he was in a hurry and ran off.
...Then you came straight to the Hideout.
That's right! You guys believe me now?
If what Ririn said is true...
It IS true!
Calm down. Nobody's doubtin' ya.
As far as I know, the Liberators all used the demon summoning app to summon demons...
Maybe it's some kind of new tech developed by the Acolytes?
Nope. I've never heard of anything like that, so no.
Hey, you're here? When did you come in?
I was here from the start.
The Acolytes did a lot of research on the demon summoning app,
but they learned nothing. Nobody knows how it works or who made it.
Tell me about it. I've done some digging on my own from time to time, but never found anything...
Besides, if that guy was an Acolyte,
he'd try to kill you during the chaos of the fight.
Whoa... Come to think of it, I shoulda been more careful with that...
So the guy I met was...
A demon.
From some other organization.
That is a possibility.
Demons don't need smartphones to summon other demons. We know that much from experience.
So, a third organization besides the Liberators and the Acolytes...
It's plausible.
Well whoever that guy was, if he can summon demons, we gotta know what he's after just in case.
So I guess we got some investigatin' to do y'all.
Aight, here's the plan. Me and Shiang Sun will stay here to see what we can find on the internet and social media.
Everyone else, ask around in the streets.
If you find anything, report in.
Everyone know what they're supposed to do? Aight then, let's get to it!
...And that is what is going on.
You are not oblivious to these foolish acts made by certain humans I presume.
Yes, this situation is most unfortunate...
That is why we have decided to eradicate these impudent humans in the name of God.
We hope that you will aid us in the upcoming conflict.
Why have you decided this on your own?
We have been charged with the task of vanquishing evil. We are the Lord's weapons of justice.
Therefor we must destroy all those foolish enough to oppose Him.
It is what the Lord created us for.
We are just doing our duty, even though He is not here to issue the command.
Come. Let us ride to war. For the glory of God!
